@startuml
skinparam DefaultFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam ActivityBorderThickness 2
title <b>Final Response and Error Handling</b>

(C)

:<b>Return 200</b>\n<b>{success: true, message: "Attendance marked successfully"}</b>;
stop

note right
  <b>Global Error Handling (wraps entire process):</b>
  Any thrown error from earlier steps
  (missing history, missing schedule, DB
  failure, etc.) is caught here.
  Logged server-side, then:
  Return 500 {success: false, message: err.message}
end note

@enduml
